    <br>
    MISSION STATMENT <br> <br> 
  
   Disaster Buddy's mission is to promote natural disaster safety, security, and proper safety protocols. With many natural disasters occuring in our world, this website provides valuable information regarding natural disaster safety in the United States. 

    </div>
    
    <div id = "secondAbout"; style="height:1000px;color:white;text-align:center;background-color:#6e62ad;font-size:36px">
    <br>
     ABOUT <br> <br>
     Disaster Buddy provides all people in the United States of America, with
     proper protocol and safety lessons for the most common natural disasters in
     the USA. These include droughts, floods, earthquakes, volcanic eruptions thunderstorms,
     tornadoes, hurricanes, and fires. By providing users with disaster
     information, safety lessons, statistics, and knowledge quizzes, Disaster
     Buddy aims to supply people with the utmost knowledge of these disasters to
     ensure safety for all in the case that these disasters were to happen.
